      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"varik\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"4347\" data-full=\"true\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/varik/48/115_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> varik:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Keshtu demtohet ekonomia e vendit</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>por mbrohet shendeti i njerzeve.<br>\nAjo qe me gezoi, eshte qe organet e shtetit fuksionojne, kontrrollet jane rritur e vazhdojne.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 2,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77729,
      "post_number": 5,
      "username": "varik",
      "name": "varianti kohor",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/varik/{size}/115_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T01:09:00.407Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Per ata qe nuk paguajne rryshfetin, te tjeret jo te skaduar, por edhe te kalbura jane ok</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 4,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77730,
      "post_number": 6,
      "username": "Edison",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/97f17d/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T01:18:51.047Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Problem eshte skanimi.me.rreze te demshme neper dogana. Rastet e kancerit jane shtuar ndjeshem.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77731,
      "post_number": 7,
      "username": "InkuizitoriMoth",
      "name": "..... ......",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/inkuizitorimoth/{size}/7035_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T04:17:46.306Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Pjer, pse nuk shkruan me tregime udhetimi? Ka vdekur Uliksi brenda teje? Apo nuk e gjen më ku eshte Itaka? Apo je duke pallu Çirçen? Te ka shndrruar Çirçeja ne derr?</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77734,
      "post_number": 8,
      "username": "Pjer",
      "name": "Pjer Thomas",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T14:45:17.951Z",
      "cooked": "<p>i modho, pershtypjet e maj-qershorit 2018, akoma nuk i kam shkruar, se kisha hallin e dy librave te mij qe dalin tani, si dhe ca halle te tjera.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 7,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77735,
      "post_number": 9,
      "username": "Pjer",
      "name": "Pjer Thomas",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T14:48:59.567Z",
      "cooked": "<p>variko, rryshfeti fuksionon kur ke te besh me nje person, por jo kur ke te besh me dy-tre persona,</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 5,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77736,
      "post_number": 10,
      "username": "varik",
      "name": "varianti kohor",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/varik/{size}/115_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T16:04:19.319Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ne albanistan po paguve shefin, argatet mbyllin syte</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 9,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77737,
      "post_number": 11,
      "username": "InkuizitoriMoth",
      "name": "..... ......",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/inkuizitorimoth/{size}/7035_2.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T16:10:34.201Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Çirçe eshte eshte nje menyre te theni per te treguar fenomenin e pergjithishem te shndrrimit te njeriut ne derr.<br>\nNe veçanti fenomeni mund te jete qe Çirçeja eshte shtepia botuese qe shnderron ne derr ke boton.<br>\nFenomeni arrin deri atje sa ka vertet shtepi botuese qe ka emrin “Shtepia Botuese  Çirçe”, siç ishte dikur “Shtepia Botuese Naim Frasheri”.</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 8,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 77739,
      "post_number": 12,
      "username": "Pjer",
      "name": "Pjer Thomas",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-15T16:25:26.659Z",
      "cooked": "<p>jo-jo variko, kane ardhur kohera te tjera, ku shefi ka frike nga mvartesi, biles kjo gje, kjo psikollogji, kish filluar qysh ne kohen e  buall mavrise,</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 10,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
